413 representing lived experience, a member representing lived experience or the board with
424 which the member is associated may apply for compensation from the Secretary of State.
435 The Secretary of State is required to develop, as necessary, policies or procedures to
446 prioritize compensation for members representing lived experience, and compensation is
457 only allowable to the extent that funding is available.
